summary: An MSc graduate of Clinical Psychology at Leiden University, BSc graduate at EKPA, and SNF Scholar for parallel studies in Sociology at DEREE. Full SNF Scholarship for study abroad semester in the USA, University of Virginia. Interested in Clinical Psychology, Counseling, and Psychotherapy. EFPSA Soft Skills Trainer and Researcher on E-Mental Health and Behavioral Policies. Work and volunteering experience. Skilled in organizing, multitasking, teamwork, working under pressure. Traveling, dancing, laughing, and getting out of her comfort zone enthusiast.
